&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>14:21:43&lt;span class="o">]&lt;/span>: This setup will &lt;span class="nb">help&lt;/span> you get up and running in no time.
